thread.title: Youth festival begins

author: tribuneindia.com
title: Youth festival begins
text:
Yamunanagar, October 18
The three-day Zonal Youth Festival (Yamunanagar zone) began at DAV College for Girls, Yamunanagar, on Sunday. Haryana Assembly Speaker Kanwar Pal Gurjar was the chief guest at the inaugural session and Director, Youth Cultural Affairs of Kurukshetra University, Dr Maha Singh Poonia, was the guest of honour. The Speaker spoke about the growing needs to revive interest in music. Dr Sushma Arya, principal of the college, said competitions were held at four venues simultaneously comprising Jhankar, Abhivyakti, Sargam and Haryanvi Kala Manch.â€” TNS
